<h1> Add page transitions </h1> 

<li>1. Select spreads that you wish to apply transitions in the pages panel. </li>
<li>2. To display the Page Transitons panel, select Window > Interactive > Page Transitions. </li>
<li>3. Choose a transition from the transition menu and customize with the Direction and Speed menus. </li>
<li>4. To apply to all spreads, choose Apply to All Spreads in the Transition panel </li>

</html> 